Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:51.11,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}玄関前ですぐに気づいてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.03,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1\move(300,15,45,15)}ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.15,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}鼻息荒げフガフガ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:59.24,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}廊下すたこら駆けてくるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今夜は君の大好物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.42,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}これ食べたかったんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.50,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}そうこれこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:11.59,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}君が揃えばこれで完璧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:16.01,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}ごちそうとみんなで待ってたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.01,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}アイ・アム・ア　エプロンボーイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:24.68,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}エプロンボーイ　技を繰り出せキッチン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.15,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}アイ・アム・ア　エプロンボーイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:32.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,0)}エプロンボーイ　君の笑顔は絶品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.11,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我が家の団欒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.40,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}笑い声満タン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.53,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}お茶の間ワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.57,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}涎の出てて　洗ったのお手々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}Are you ready？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.53,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.02,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}你的鼻子真好使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:51.11,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}在过道里就注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.03,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1\move(300,1065,45,1065)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.15,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}哼哼喘着粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:59.24,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}沿着走廊一阵风跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.42,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.50,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:11.59,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:16.01,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:20.01,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:24.68,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}围裙男孩 在厨房放连招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.15,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:32.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,0)}围裙男孩 你的笑容是绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.11,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我们家团团圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.40,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}笑声满满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.53,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}客厅活像乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.57,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}流着口水 洗好小手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.87,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}Are you ready？
